  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with reasonable suspicion of bronchial carcinoma or histologically proven
             bronchial carcinoma, which has not been medicated until the study entry and

          -  Patients with sleep apnea who had recently been diagnosed with bronchial carcinoma.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy

          -  other already known malignancies or tumors

          -  Patients with non-invasive artificial respiration due to a chronic respiratory
             insufficiencies
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
